00:44:04,879 --> 00:44:06,840
And, you know, it was a very sad day for me.

602
00:44:06,860 --> 00:44:07,700
Charlie was a mentor.

603
00:44:07,720 --> 00:44:08,501
Charlie was a friend.

604
00:44:08,881 --> 00:44:10,102
And Charlie gave me a chance.

